On the fourth `` run '' with <COREF ID="19" TYPE="IDENT">the borrowed rod</COREF> , <COREF ID="0" TYPE="IDENT">the experiment</COREF> began producing excess heat .
<COREF ID="0" TYPE="IDENT">The experiment</COREF> was stopped briefly to change an instrument .
When <COREF ID="0" TYPE="IDENT">it</COREF> was restarted , heat output `` really took off '' and produced excess heat for several hours before dying down , <COREF ID="42" TYPE="IDENT">he</COREF> said .
Typical of other experiments , <COREF ID="42" TYPE="IDENT">Mr. Oriani</COREF> said <COREF ID="0" TYPE="IDENT"><COREF ID="42" TYPE="IDENT">his</COREF> experiment</COREF> was `` very erratic . ''
