<COREF ID="10" TYPE="IDENT">Mr. Bockris</COREF> previously reported getting <COREF ID="21" TYPE="IDENT">bursts of excess heat</COREF> and of detecting <COREF ID="9" TYPE="IDENT">increasing amounts of tritium forming in <COREF ID="36" TYPE="IDENT">the heavy water</COREF></COREF> .
