<COREF ID="34" TYPE="IDENT">Messrs. <COREF ID="38" TYPE="IDENT">Fleischmann</COREF> and <COREF ID="11" TYPE="IDENT">Pons</COREF></COREF> initially reported indirect evidence of neutrons being produced in <COREF ID="34" TYPE="IDENT">their</COREF> experiment but later conceded the measurements were questionable .
